{
  "stem": "24544.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He came he with us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And June 13, when we arrived to Auschwitz, it was selected any way, men side and woman side.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he went with my father's second cousin, an older man.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we never, ever saw him again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But when we were taken to the bath, shower, water where once a month, in Auschwitz from Birkenau, we always walked between the camps.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it was sure fence all over.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we were calling our relatives' name.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we know he was in the gypsy lager.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The gypsy has a special lager.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that gypsy lager, the first two weeks, all of the tent or something like that was evacuated.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was terrible, because the gypsies was living over there long time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they knew what happens.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were over there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We smell the gas chamber, and we didn't know what was going on.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Nobody knows.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And when all Polish kapos who was living there four, five years, they said to us, keep quiet, because your parents is going up over there in the smoke.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Like they speak French, we don't know a-- a single word about it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We just saw leave bushes, very tall, two lines.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we saw a terrible chimney, tall, or two, I'm not sure.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we-- we felt the smoke.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I told my mother, because we have grape yard.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And when we went to harvest the grapes, we roasted lambs.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And that was the smell over there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Over there was lots of trees, [INAUDIBLE], like the Christmas trees, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Evergreen.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the Evergreen has a special movement.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's always moving.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It doesn't need any wind.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that took the smell--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right and left and everywhere.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
